   - $\phi(q(r_1) \cdot q(r_2)) = \phi(q(r_1 \cdot r_2)) = f(r_1 \cdot r_2) = f(r_1) \cdot f(r_2) = \phi(q(r_1)) \cdot \phi(q(r_2))$
   
